WEBVTT

00:00:02.043 --> 00:00:04.546
WRITTEN BY HYUGA NATSU

00:01:32.133 --> 00:01:33.383
{\an8}THIS STORY IS A FICTION AND ALL NAMES OF
FIGURES AND ORGANIZATIONS ARE FICTITIOUS.

00:01:33.384 --> 00:01:34.844
{\an8}MOREOVER, THE STORY HAS NO RELATION
TO REAL-LIFE INCIDENTS AND EVENTS.

00:01:36.846 --> 00:01:37.722
Lady Loulan.

00:01:50.360 --> 00:01:52.194
<i>It seems the resurrection medicine</i>

00:01:52.195 --> 00:01:56.157
<i>was actually an experiment during
the development of an immortality elixir.</i>

00:01:57.283 --> 00:02:00.662
<i>In fact, Suirei was brought back to life
with that medicine.</i>

00:02:01.412 --> 00:02:03.748
<i>The previous apothecary
really was skilled.</i>

00:02:05.291 --> 00:02:07.584
<i>But what Shenmei wants
is an immortality drug</i>

00:02:07.585 --> 00:02:09.336
<i>that makes you look ten years younger</i>

00:02:09.337 --> 00:02:11.673
<i>with just one dose.</i>

00:02:16.594 --> 00:02:18.596
You've got it rough too.

00:02:20.682 --> 00:02:22.766
No such medicine exists.

00:02:22.767 --> 00:02:24.936
I know that...

00:02:26.187 --> 00:02:28.898
But even I have my pride as an apothecary!

00:02:51.296 --> 00:02:53.506
<i>The days just keep slipping by.</i>

00:02:56.134 --> 00:02:57.635
Wait for me!

00:02:58.219 --> 00:02:59.136
Young master!

00:02:59.137 --> 00:03:01.471
How many times have I told you
not to go that way?

00:03:01.472 --> 00:03:03.016
It's fine, who cares!

00:03:05.184 --> 00:03:07.311
<i>Getting scolded again, huh?</i>

00:03:07.312 --> 00:03:10.607
<i>He gets dragged back every time,
but he never gets tired of it.</i>

00:03:13.443 --> 00:03:15.611
<i>And this smell...</i>

00:03:15.612 --> 00:03:18.280
<i>Is there a workshop down below?</i>

00:03:18.281 --> 00:03:20.074
<i>Like in that hidden village.</i>

00:03:23.745 --> 00:03:25.997
<i>I hope nothing explodes.</i>

00:03:31.127 --> 00:03:32.003
<i>Hmm?</i>

00:03:35.340 --> 00:03:37.049
<i>Wire?</i>

00:03:37.050 --> 00:03:39.969
<i>"Run. The guard will be lured away."</i>

00:03:40.553 --> 00:03:43.223
<i>Run? But where to?</i>

00:03:44.849 --> 00:03:47.644
- Let me go!
- Hey! Young master!

00:03:49.812 --> 00:03:51.231
Was this your doing?

00:03:53.816 --> 00:03:55.317
"Lured away"?

00:03:55.318 --> 00:03:56.611
Hey.

00:04:01.407 --> 00:04:03.451
{\an8}What are you up to?

00:04:04.077 --> 00:04:05.578
What do you mean?

00:04:06.663 --> 00:04:07.997
Did you put them up to this?

00:04:08.998 --> 00:04:10.416
No idea what you mean.

00:04:12.126 --> 00:04:15.088
<i>He was trying to help me
in his own childish way.</i>

00:04:15.880 --> 00:04:17.798
<i>It might've been naive,</i>

00:04:17.799 --> 00:04:20.385
<i>but if we got caught, it'd be serious.</i>

00:04:23.388 --> 00:04:25.806
I was just playing.

00:04:25.807 --> 00:04:28.393
And while I was at it,
I checked if the guards were slacking off.

00:04:29.936 --> 00:04:31.813
- Is that true?
- Yes.

00:04:33.898 --> 00:04:35.942
Do not do anything suspicious again.

00:04:36.734 --> 00:04:39.487
- Got it!
- Wait, but I'm sure.

00:04:40.071 --> 00:04:42.031
Do not cause any more fuss.

00:04:42.573 --> 00:04:43.533
You understand?

00:04:45.576 --> 00:04:46.953
Fine.

00:04:49.372 --> 00:04:51.915
<i>I'm glad Suirei was there.</i>

00:04:51.916 --> 00:04:54.585
<i>- All's well that ends well.</i>
- Oh my?

00:05:00.174 --> 00:05:02.468
What is all this commotion?

00:05:03.386 --> 00:05:04.220
Mother.

00:05:10.351 --> 00:05:11.602
Mother.

00:05:12.228 --> 00:05:14.104
It is nothing serious.

00:05:14.105 --> 00:05:15.731
Really?

00:05:15.732 --> 00:05:18.066
Then why is the apothecary outside?

00:05:18.067 --> 00:05:19.985
I wonder.

00:05:19.986 --> 00:05:21.028
Kyou-u was playing

00:05:21.029 --> 00:05:24.157
in front of the apothecary's room
and interfering with the guard.

00:05:24.949 --> 00:05:26.616
Just in case, I was asking about that.

00:05:26.617 --> 00:05:27.660
Oh dear,

00:05:28.536 --> 00:05:31.246
did you do something bad?

00:05:31.247 --> 00:05:32.789
That's not good.

00:05:32.790 --> 00:05:35.834
If you do not behave,

00:05:35.835 --> 00:05:37.627
I might have to

00:05:37.628 --> 00:05:40.465
spank you a little, hmm?

00:05:43.634 --> 00:05:45.344
Lady Shenmei, that is...

00:05:45.928 --> 00:05:47.263
What?

00:05:48.431 --> 00:05:50.599
Kyou-u is still a child.

00:05:50.600 --> 00:05:52.602
And it really was not

00:05:53.102 --> 00:05:54.145
anything serious.

00:06:02.820 --> 00:06:04.404
So someone made a big fuss

00:06:04.405 --> 00:06:07.866
over something trivial,
is that what you're saying?

00:06:07.867 --> 00:06:09.660
No way! That's not true!

00:06:10.995 --> 00:06:13.789
But doesn't it seem that way?

00:06:13.790 --> 00:06:16.374
The water prison
should give him time to think.

00:06:16.375 --> 00:06:19.003
- No!
<i>- This is absurd.</i>

00:06:19.587 --> 00:06:21.798
<i>The reason doesn't matter.</i>

00:06:22.673 --> 00:06:24.758
<i>She just enjoys</i>

00:06:24.759 --> 00:06:26.469
<i>making others suffer.</i>

00:06:27.428 --> 00:06:28.929
<i>It has nothing to do with me.</i>

00:06:28.930 --> 00:06:32.350
<i>I should leave the guard and Kyou-u alone.</i>

00:06:34.227 --> 00:06:35.353
<i>But,</i>

00:06:35.937 --> 00:06:37.229
<i>it pisses me off.</i>

00:06:37.230 --> 00:06:39.022
It cannot be helped.

00:06:39.023 --> 00:06:42.025
Then let us punish both of them.

00:06:42.026 --> 00:06:43.528
You damn hag.

00:06:44.821 --> 00:06:46.155
What?

00:06:49.367 --> 00:06:50.409
You little brat!

00:06:53.871 --> 00:06:55.039
<i>That was dumb.</i>

00:06:59.544 --> 00:07:01.129
I asked him to.

00:07:04.924 --> 00:07:06.843
I asked that child to help me escape.

00:07:07.468 --> 00:07:10.096
It was my request.

00:07:10.680 --> 00:07:11.973
{\an8}You!

00:07:13.850 --> 00:07:16.268
This apothecary is no good.

00:07:16.269 --> 00:07:18.688
Let us teach her a lesson.

00:07:19.188 --> 00:07:20.815
Throw her in the water prison!

00:07:21.983 --> 00:07:24.359
<i>In this cold? Water?</i>

00:07:24.360 --> 00:07:26.570
<i>I really should've kept quiet.</i>

00:07:26.571 --> 00:07:30.158
Then we'll lose another apothecary.

00:07:31.075 --> 00:07:32.868
Oh my, Suirei.

00:07:32.869 --> 00:07:35.036
Did I hear something?

00:07:35.037 --> 00:07:36.288
Must be my imagination.

00:07:36.289 --> 00:07:37.956
Lady Shenmei!

00:07:37.957 --> 00:07:40.001
You must not act on your own.

00:07:41.252 --> 00:07:42.795
I apologize.

00:07:43.337 --> 00:07:44.589
But--

00:07:55.600 --> 00:07:58.351
Even noble blood is worthless

00:07:58.352 --> 00:08:01.856
once it's tainted.

00:08:04.817 --> 00:08:06.151
<i>Maybe</i>

00:08:06.152 --> 00:08:08.737
<i>Suirei feels responsible in her own way.</i>

00:08:08.738 --> 00:08:12.283
I never intended to bring you this far.

00:08:13.910 --> 00:08:15.828
<i>Another fool, huh?</i>

00:08:16.746 --> 00:08:19.289
Mother.

00:08:19.290 --> 00:08:22.251
- I want to use that.
- That?

00:08:23.961 --> 00:08:26.005
You mean Taibon.

00:08:28.257 --> 00:08:29.674
<i>Taibon?</i>

00:08:29.675 --> 00:08:32.929
<i>I've heard of that before.</i>

00:08:33.513 --> 00:08:36.306
Brilliant idea. Why not try it?

00:08:36.307 --> 00:08:38.768
It worked perfectly last time.

00:08:43.940 --> 00:08:45.525
<i>What now?</i>

00:08:46.025 --> 00:08:49.111
Take the apothecary with you.

00:09:01.624 --> 00:09:02.625
This way.

00:09:08.839 --> 00:09:11.509
What is this room?

00:09:13.302 --> 00:09:14.887
No hard feelings.

00:09:15.388 --> 00:09:17.056
You helped me,

00:09:17.848 --> 00:09:19.684
but this is Lady Shenmei's order.

00:09:30.069 --> 00:09:31.237
<i>Taibon.</i>

00:09:31.862 --> 00:09:34.198
<i>That's right. I remember.</i>

00:09:39.036 --> 00:09:40.912
<i>A cruel execution method</i>

00:09:40.913 --> 00:09:42.707
<i>used by a mad king in ancient times.</i>

00:09:43.583 --> 00:09:46.460
<i>A hole would be dug,
and the criminal confined within.</i>

00:09:47.128 --> 00:09:48.754
<i>And inside it were...</i>

00:09:51.048 --> 00:09:54.468
<i>No wonder. Suirei's afraid of snakes.</i>

00:10:02.435 --> 00:10:03.728
Just kidding.

00:10:04.478 --> 00:10:06.105
How adorable.

00:10:11.152 --> 00:10:13.237
What the hell?

00:10:14.363 --> 00:10:15.406
What is that?

00:10:15.906 --> 00:10:17.533
Smells kinda... toasty?

00:10:18.117 --> 00:10:20.119
Smells good.

00:10:29.003 --> 00:10:29.962
What are you doing?

00:10:33.132 --> 00:10:35.133
Do you have any salt?

00:10:35.134 --> 00:10:38.511
Of course I don't! And hey, is that?

00:10:38.512 --> 00:10:39.847
Snake.

00:10:42.933 --> 00:10:44.852
Let's pretend it's fish.

00:10:45.603 --> 00:10:47.605
But seriously, how did you even?

00:10:48.773 --> 00:10:51.858
I butchered it with a hairpin
and roasted it over a torch.

00:10:51.859 --> 00:10:54.194
You're seriously okay with that?

00:10:54.195 --> 00:10:57.740
Snakes and bugs move slowly
before hibernation.

00:10:58.532 --> 00:11:01.618
Just in case,
I killed any venomous ones first

00:11:01.619 --> 00:11:03.745
and turned my herbs into ash

00:11:03.746 --> 00:11:05.830
- for insect repellent.
- Was there even

00:11:05.831 --> 00:11:07.458
a point in me coming here?

00:11:08.668 --> 00:11:11.170
So, what do you need from me?

00:11:12.213 --> 00:11:14.964
Suirei and the kid
asked me to help you out.

00:11:14.965 --> 00:11:17.301
<i>Said to give you a hand.</i>

00:11:17.885 --> 00:11:19.052
<i>That kid</i>

00:11:19.053 --> 00:11:21.680
<i>even gave me a jade hair ornament.</i>

00:11:22.515 --> 00:11:23.932
<i>Thanks to you,</i>

00:11:23.933 --> 00:11:26.352
<i>we didn't get punished.</i>

00:11:27.561 --> 00:11:28.562
They did that?

00:11:29.897 --> 00:11:32.649
Man, I'm done with this place.

00:11:32.650 --> 00:11:34.360
I saw a smoke signal outside.

00:11:35.444 --> 00:11:37.988
<i>It means a punitive force
is coming from the capital.</i>

00:11:38.656 --> 00:11:40.241
<i>The whole fortress is in chaos.</i>

00:11:41.033 --> 00:11:43.202
- That's how I was able to sneak in.
- <i>Huh? This smell.</i>

00:11:43.786 --> 00:11:45.204
I'm leaving now.

00:11:45.913 --> 00:11:49.124
If you're planning on running,
don't take the stairs on the other side.

00:11:49.125 --> 00:11:52.043
They're making gunpowder in the basement.

00:11:52.044 --> 00:11:53.044
Gunpowder.

00:11:53.045 --> 00:11:55.004
There are a lot of people down there.

00:11:55.005 --> 00:11:58.466
- If it explodes, you'll get caught in it--
- Thank you!

00:11:58.467 --> 00:12:00.136
Got it. The opposite stairs!

00:12:01.429 --> 00:12:03.556
I warned you, okay!

00:12:22.491 --> 00:12:24.660
<i>So that smell was from there.</i>

00:12:25.494 --> 00:12:28.205
<i>It really is gunpowder.</i>

00:12:29.206 --> 00:12:30.623
<i>But this smoke,</i>

00:12:30.624 --> 00:12:33.126
<i>they'll get poisoned like this.</i>

00:12:33.127 --> 00:12:34.377
<i>Using fire near gunpowder?</i>

00:12:34.378 --> 00:12:37.047
<i>That's insane.</i>

00:12:38.215 --> 00:12:39.049
<i>Oh no.</i>

00:12:41.135 --> 00:12:42.094
<i>That is...</i>

00:12:46.432 --> 00:12:48.225
Leave this place immediately!

00:12:49.685 --> 00:12:51.187
What's wrong, Milady?

00:12:51.812 --> 00:12:54.272
The punitive force will be here
any moment.

00:12:54.273 --> 00:12:57.400
This fortress will become
a battlefield and fall.

00:12:57.401 --> 00:12:59.195
You must escape before that!

00:13:01.906 --> 00:13:02.948
Silver!

00:13:04.617 --> 00:13:06.452
Waah!

00:13:07.411 --> 00:13:09.330
Waah!

00:13:10.456 --> 00:13:11.332
Yes!

00:13:11.916 --> 00:13:12.832
Yeah!

00:13:12.833 --> 00:13:14.667
M... Milady?

00:13:14.668 --> 00:13:15.836
You too, hurry!

00:13:20.341 --> 00:13:21.509
Do your best to get out!

00:13:24.094 --> 00:13:24.970
Get out of here!

00:13:28.516 --> 00:13:30.100
<i>Are you serious?</i>

00:13:51.872 --> 00:13:52.957
This is bad!

00:13:54.833 --> 00:13:55.876
<i>Loulan.</i>

00:14:01.799 --> 00:14:02.758
Loulan!

00:14:03.926 --> 00:14:07.012
Huh! Maomao, what are you doing here?

00:14:07.596 --> 00:14:09.265
I should be asking you that.

00:14:10.266 --> 00:14:12.642
Are you hurt?

00:14:12.643 --> 00:14:15.145
I figured you'd be fine with the Taibon.

00:14:15.771 --> 00:14:16.939
<i>I knew it.</i>

00:14:19.441 --> 00:14:20.276
It was delicious.

00:14:22.111 --> 00:14:24.113
{\an8}That makes no sense.

00:14:24.822 --> 00:14:27.574
Not coming from someone
who eats bugs on purpose.

00:14:27.575 --> 00:14:28.576
Hey!

00:14:31.620 --> 00:14:34.623
Let's get out of the fortress.
The punitive force is coming.

00:14:35.124 --> 00:14:36.166
We have to go now.

00:14:41.630 --> 00:14:42.798
I am not going.

00:14:44.550 --> 00:14:46.176
I still have things to do.

00:14:59.189 --> 00:15:00.857
You're coming with me?

00:15:00.858 --> 00:15:02.818
You could still escape.

00:15:03.444 --> 00:15:04.820
I know I'm being foolish.

00:15:05.404 --> 00:15:07.739
If my mother finds out,
it will be terrifying.

00:15:07.740 --> 00:15:10.159
If I get away with just a whipping,
I'll be lucky.

00:15:10.910 --> 00:15:14.163
I thought you were being treated
with care.

00:15:19.001 --> 00:15:20.210
Mother barely even

00:15:20.836 --> 00:15:23.255
remembers what I look like.

00:15:24.381 --> 00:15:26.507
Ever since I can remember,

00:15:26.508 --> 00:15:29.428
I was made up with rouge and powder.

00:15:30.471 --> 00:15:33.307
To Mother, I'm just a doll.

00:15:34.600 --> 00:15:35.601
A cute doll

00:15:36.143 --> 00:15:38.437
who always obeys.

00:15:39.521 --> 00:15:40.731
So...

00:15:41.690 --> 00:15:43.399
Oh, sister!

00:15:43.400 --> 00:15:46.320
- You again?
- I want to help too!

00:15:46.904 --> 00:15:48.405
I want to be with you, sister!

00:15:48.906 --> 00:15:50.282
What are you slacking off for?

00:15:52.785 --> 00:15:53.661
M... Mother?

00:15:56.413 --> 00:15:58.040
Bring the tea at once!

00:15:59.917 --> 00:16:01.084
<i>She did not even</i>

00:16:01.085 --> 00:16:03.544
<i>recognize me in maid clothes.</i>

00:16:03.545 --> 00:16:05.756
She hit me with a fan across the cheek.

00:16:06.256 --> 00:16:08.299
When I dressed as a maid,

00:16:08.300 --> 00:16:10.302
I was just another servant to her.

00:16:11.303 --> 00:16:14.055
And yet, you still went to see Suirei.

00:16:14.056 --> 00:16:17.351
Because I wanted to be close to her.

00:16:19.103 --> 00:16:23.273
{\an8}She was always being tormented by Mother.

00:16:23.774 --> 00:16:26.067
{\an8}I think her mother died

00:16:26.068 --> 00:16:28.404
{\an8}from being tormented by mine.

00:16:31.031 --> 00:16:33.367
<i>When Father took Suirei in,</i>

00:16:33.909 --> 00:16:35.410
<i>Mother flew into a rage,</i>

00:16:35.411 --> 00:16:38.287
<i>hair disheveled,</i>

00:16:38.288 --> 00:16:41.874
<i>screaming, "Will you mock me
across two generations?"</i>

00:16:41.875 --> 00:16:44.837
<i>"That daughter's nothing
but a shameless whore."</i>

00:16:46.797 --> 00:16:48.215
It was like hell.

00:16:49.466 --> 00:16:51.218
<i>Two generations.</i>

00:16:52.177 --> 00:16:53.720
By the time

00:16:53.721 --> 00:16:56.515
I was sent back as a gift,

00:16:57.099 --> 00:17:00.018
<i>my mother and I
were already by Father's side.</i>

00:17:00.019 --> 00:17:02.855
Even noble blood is worthless

00:17:03.397 --> 00:17:06.025
once it's tainted.

00:17:07.609 --> 00:17:09.403
Suirei. Could she be?

00:17:10.863 --> 00:17:12.698
Have you never heard the rumors?

00:17:13.282 --> 00:17:15.325
About the woman

00:17:15.993 --> 00:17:17.744
who bore the previous emperor's

00:17:17.745 --> 00:17:20.247
first child and was then
separated from her?

00:17:20.748 --> 00:17:23.292
I think she died last year, right?

00:17:23.876 --> 00:17:26.920
Yes. That woman was Sister's grandmother.

00:17:27.588 --> 00:17:28.922
<i>Her name was Taihou.</i>

00:17:29.715 --> 00:17:32.801
<i>She used to be an attendant
when my mother was in the inner palace.</i>

00:17:34.678 --> 00:17:35.846
<i>I knew it.</i>

00:17:36.513 --> 00:17:37.680
And

00:17:37.681 --> 00:17:41.559
Sister's mother was the daughter of Taihou
and the physician

00:17:41.560 --> 00:17:43.479
who was exiled from the palace.

00:17:45.147 --> 00:17:46.689
<i>So Suirei has</i>

00:17:46.690 --> 00:17:49.068
<i>royal blood running through her veins.</i>

00:17:50.611 --> 00:17:53.238
I heard she liked ghost stories.

00:17:54.239 --> 00:17:56.908
One of them nearly
choked me to death once.

00:17:56.909 --> 00:17:59.578
Maybe that was her grandmother's doing.

00:18:03.207 --> 00:18:05.250
After all, I'm my mother's daughter.

00:18:05.959 --> 00:18:08.045
She must have hated me.

00:18:08.796 --> 00:18:11.798
Hated me enough to want to kill me,
even as a ghost.

00:18:11.799 --> 00:18:14.676
Who knows if ghosts even exist?

00:18:15.552 --> 00:18:17.012
That sounds like you.

00:18:20.849 --> 00:18:23.851
Mother married Father just to

00:18:23.852 --> 00:18:25.938
give birth to me, Loulan.

00:18:26.897 --> 00:18:29.066
It was only for revenge.

00:18:30.484 --> 00:18:33.112
Father has Western blood,

00:18:33.904 --> 00:18:36.240
same as the Queen Mother.

00:18:37.741 --> 00:18:38.866
<i>So,</i>

00:18:38.867 --> 00:18:41.161
<i>Loulan's eyes...</i>

00:18:45.207 --> 00:18:48.209
"You will be the new Queen Mother,"

00:18:48.210 --> 00:18:50.295
she always told me.

00:18:51.964 --> 00:18:53.215
Hey.

00:18:54.550 --> 00:18:57.511
<i>Loulan or Shisui.</i>

00:18:58.387 --> 00:19:01.181
<i>I do not even know
what to call you anymore,</i>

00:19:02.349 --> 00:19:03.642
<i>But...</i>

00:19:08.939 --> 00:19:10.023
<i>But...</i>

00:19:11.650 --> 00:19:12.734
Shisui.

00:19:22.161 --> 00:19:23.203
What is it?

00:19:26.081 --> 00:19:29.250
The abortifacient ingredients
that were circulating in the rear palace.

00:19:29.251 --> 00:19:30.711
Did you have some?

00:19:31.545 --> 00:19:32.921
To use on yourself?

00:19:34.548 --> 00:19:37.425
That ghost story you told me before,

00:19:37.426 --> 00:19:40.137
the one where the bell cricket's wife
eats her husband.

00:19:41.555 --> 00:19:43.891
Were you talking about yourself?

00:19:44.808 --> 00:19:48.604
Comparing yourself to an insect
trapped in a cage called "nobility,"

00:19:49.146 --> 00:19:52.316
doomed to bear a child
and devour the emperor,

00:19:52.983 --> 00:19:56.361
<i>but you were afraid of that fate.</i>

00:19:57.946 --> 00:19:59.156
The lantern plant.

00:20:00.032 --> 00:20:00.908
I know.

00:20:02.451 --> 00:20:04.703
Maomao, you are so sharp.

00:20:06.747 --> 00:20:08.749
I am glad I brought you here.

00:20:14.296 --> 00:20:16.381
Seriously, you toss and turn too much.

00:20:26.808 --> 00:20:28.769
They are not breathing.

00:20:29.394 --> 00:20:30.896
What?

00:20:35.692 --> 00:20:36.610
You gave them

00:20:37.194 --> 00:20:38.737
poison?

00:20:54.211 --> 00:20:55.087
Medicine.

00:20:59.091 --> 00:21:01.717
What I did was already extreme enough.

00:21:01.718 --> 00:21:03.804
The whole family will be slaughtered.

00:21:04.346 --> 00:21:05.639
You can see it coming.

00:21:08.392 --> 00:21:10.852
{\an8}I mixed it in sweet juice
and gave it to them

00:21:11.895 --> 00:21:13.897
{\an8}after we looked at picture scrolls.

00:21:15.732 --> 00:21:18.860
<i>One of the girls cried,
saying she wanted to sleep with her mom.</i>

00:21:19.653 --> 00:21:21.238
<i>But she could not.</i>

00:21:21.863 --> 00:21:23.448
<i>Their mothers were</i>

00:21:24.366 --> 00:21:26.952
<i>all close with mine.</i>

00:21:30.414 --> 00:21:31.957
The reason Kyou-u came late

00:21:32.916 --> 00:21:35.919
was because he was trying to
rescue you, Maomao.

00:21:38.171 --> 00:21:40.590
That boy, maybe he knew.

00:21:49.725 --> 00:21:51.310
<i>He bit his lip,</i>

00:21:52.102 --> 00:21:55.188
<i>and drank it all in one go.</i>

00:22:04.197 --> 00:22:06.199
Why did you bring me here?

00:23:46.091 --> 00:23:49.511
PREVIEW OF THE NEXT EPISODE

00:23:57.894 --> 00:24:00.354
{\an8}<i>The next episode is "The Forbidden Army."</i>

00:24:00.355 --> 00:24:01.898
{\an8}Subtitle translation by:
Abhishek Chand Ramola

